section:
&reftitle.install;


 &pecl.moved;
 &pecl.info;
 &url.pecl.package;mailparse.



 In order to use these functions you must compile PHP with mailparse support
 by using the --enable-mailparse configure 
 option.



 Windows users will enable php_mailparse.dll inside
 of &php.ini; in order to use these functions.
 &pecl.windows.download.avail;



 It is necessary that the mbstring
 extension is loaded before mailparse.
